snippet.title: Harpoon Lagoon - Table Arcade Redemption - IAAPA 2012
snippet.description:
Awesome, eye-catching and very addictive four player interactive video redemption arcade game played on a huge horizontally-mounted 47" HD LCD monitor with stunning graphics and simply gameplay.

PrimeTime Amusements is a global operator, seller and event renter of video arcade machines and simulators.

www.PrimeTimeAmusements.com
Video Created by Create Freely
